company_description:
BrainRocket is a global company creating end-to-end tech products for clients across Fintech, iGaming, and Marketing. ‍Young, ambitious, and unstoppable, we've already taken Cyprus, Malta, Portugal, Poland, and Serbia by storm. Our BRO team consists of 1,300 bright minds creating innovative ideas and products. We don’t follow formats. We shape them. We build what works, launch it fast, and make sure it hits.
❗️Please note that this role is office based for Valencia, Spain (RAS Valencia - Servicios Profesionales de Recursos Humanos).
❗️If you need to be relocated, we take care of the process.
We are looking for a
Founding Senior Machine Learning Engineer
to join our team. As an early hire, you will work closely with the Head of AI to
design
,
develop
, and
deploy
AI and ML solutions from the ground up
. This is a hands-on, high-visibility, and high-impact role that offers tremendous growth potential. You’ll play a
pivotal role in shaping the technical foundation of our AI team
and delivering real-world solutions in a dynamic, fast-paced environment.
✅ Responsibilities
Develop, train, and fine-tune Machine Learning and Deep Learning models for gaming and CRM use cases;
Design, build, and maintain data pipelines to ensure reliable, clean, and scalable datasets;
Collaborate with the Head of AI to transform prototypes into production-ready solutions;
Contribute to infrastructure setup, including MLOps practices, and implement CI/CD pipelines for machine learning models;
Work with cross-functional teams, including product and engineering, to integrate AI capabilities into customer-facing applications;
Document and communicate results clearly, catering to both technical and non-technical stakeholders.
✅ Requirements
A minimum of 3+ years of experience in Machine Learning, Data Engineering, or Applied AI roles;
Strong proficiency in Python and machine learning frameworks like PyTorch or TensorFlow;
Solid experience with data engineering tools (e.g., SQL, Spark, Airflow, or equivalents);
Hands-on experience with cloud platforms (AWS, GCP, or Azure);
Proven expertise in deploying ML models in production environments;
Strong problem-solving skills and the ability to work autonomously in a startup-like environment;
Excellent communication skills in English.
✅ Nice-to-Have
Experience with MLOps tools such as Docker, Kubernetes, MLflow, or Weights & Biases;
Familiarity with transformers and large language models (LLMs), particularly within the Hugging Face ecosystem;
Exposure to a variety of data types, including structured (tabular) and unstructured (text, images);
Previous experience working in the iGaming industry.
✅ What We Offer
🌴 23 days of paid vacation leave;
🏥 Six additional days of undocumented sick leaves;
🏥 Medical Insurance;
🥳 Birthdays, milestones and employee anniversaries celebrations;
🏢 Modern offices with snacks and all the essentials;
🎉 Social Club and more than 50 events per year;
🍳 Partial coverage of breakfasts and lunches;
💻 Learning and development opportunities and interesting, challenging tasks
✈️ Relocation package (tickets, staying in a hotel for up to 2 weeks, and visa relocation support for our employees and their family members);
📚 Opportunity to develop language skills, with partial compensation for the cost of English;
📈 Competitive remuneration level with annual review;
🤝 Teambuilding activities.
Bold moves start here. Make yours. Apply today!
By submitting your application, you agree to our Privacy Policy.

